attributes.best_description:
ADULT PICK UP

Morning 6am Skate:

  • Full gear required   
  • $12.00 per person

ADULT PICK UP HOCKEY

Drop in hockey opportunity.

Pre-Registration encouraged to secure your space.

Please keep in mind that walk up space may not be available and may not be able to enter the ice pending online registration rosters.

PICK UP CANCELLATION NOTICE:
Cancellations/transfers must be emailed to Jenny, Tyler, or Anna day before the skate. No phone calls, texts, or Messenger will be accepted.
Emails to send cancellation request must be received 24 hours prior to scheduled session:
Jennyg@xicenter.com
TylerL@xicenter.com
Anna@xicenter.com

** Goalies will be charged unless they email the staff the day prior, to allow other goalies to register.
** Phone calls will not be accepted as notice of cancellation.
